==English==
===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-interrupt.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|interrupt||}}

# to [[disturb]] or [[halt]] an [[ongoing]] [[process]] or [[action]] by [[interfere|interfering]] [[sudden]]ly
#:''A maverick politician repeatedly '''interrupted''' the debate by shouting.''
# (''computing'') To assert to a [[computer]] that an exceptional condition must be handled.
#:''The [[packet]] receiver circuit '''interrupted''' the microprocessor.''

====Synonyms====
#[[continue]], [[resume]]

